    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty. It\u2019s honestly like it just rolled right off the showroom floor\u2014absolutely flawless inside and out! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it still has that fresh feel and drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s essentially brand new and ready for its next adventure, this is the one for you. Come take it for a spin, you\u2019re going to love it!",
