    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This FD3S is a superlative example of Japanese engineering, featuring the iconic 13B-REW sequential twin-turbocharged rotary engine. The chassis exhibits zero torsional fatigue, retaining its factory-spec 50/50 weight distribution and aluminum double-wishbone suspension for surgical turn-in. Recent compression tests confirm the apex seals are well within factory tolerances, ensuring optimal thermal efficiency. Mated to a crisp five-speed manual and a Torsen limited-slip differential, the drivetrain remains unmolested and mechanically flawless. Finished in its original paint with an immaculate interior, this is a turn-key collector piece for the discerning purist seeking peak analog performance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
