    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presented here is a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, having been meticulously stored in a climate-controlled environment and driven only on fair-weather weekends. The exterior paint retains its original factory luster, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating with absolutely zero rock chips, swirls, or imperfections to be found. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium leather upholstery remains supple without a single crease on the bolsters, and the original factory scent persists. Every electronic component, switch, and dial functions with crisp precision. Mechanically, the car is flawless, backed by a comprehensive binder of service records performed exclusively by certified technicians. The engine bay is clean enough to eat off of, and the undercarriage shows no signs of road wear. This is not just a used car; it is a collector-grade investment for the most discerning enthusiast who demands perfection.",
      "price": 46500.0,
